        "timestamp": "2019-03-20 20:01:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\n> (20 comments)\n > \n > I am Ok with this code from the perspective that is an improvement\n > over the current base which already had many issues.   I still\n > think there are many issues but considering that most of them are\n > inherited and there are improvements I am willing to accept. If you\n > can go over the list of coments Praveen and provide comments it it\n > is existing issue or newly introduced.  I am ok with dealing only\n > with newly introduced issues for the reason I mentioned above.\n\nYou might want to use EntityTransCloser in policy/common/utils; it can be used to manage a transaction via try-with-resources.",
        "patchset_number": 11
